Cell["\<\
Suppose that we make a measurement of the Pauli Z operator. This gives an \
idea what would happen after the measurement. There are two possible outcomes \
0 (corresponding to eigenvalue 1 of Z) and 1 (corresponding to eigenvalue -1 \
of Z). Each associated list shows the probability and post-measurement state.\
\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->2143767083,ExpressionUUID->"8ad1b9a4-d07b-45c0-89d0-494ccac4d5e1"],

