Pauli string or a matrix representing a Pauli string. Measurement[op][vec] or \
Measurement[op] ** vec returns a vector resulting from the measurement on \
state vec. The measurement readout can be accessed with Readout[op]. \
Measurement[{op1, op2, ..., opn}][vec] is \
Measurement[op1][Measurement[op2][... Measurement[opn][vec]]].", 
